{
  "stem": "18572.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 296.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So while he couldn't come up to play with me, we would sort of have signals of playing through the window of this attic.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With clothes?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know what happened with clothes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember having-- it sounds awful, but in the forest, always having lice, you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER] Sitting there, trying to get rid of the lice-- but I don't know what I did for clothing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When we were in hiding with this Czech man who kept us for most of the winter, there was some point where he became uneasy, and he felt that he couldn't hide us anymore.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And somewhere along that-- the line or at-- around this point, my mother decided to go back to Mizoch.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in-- in the backyard, somewhere where our house had been, my father had hidden some money and some valuables.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she decided that if she went back there and got some of these, maybe she could pay someone to keep us.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he apparently drew a map for her or whatever.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we went back to the village.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- So she took you with her when she went back?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, because we left--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--this Czech man.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she hid me somewhere.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I thought it was like a shed of some sort.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She says it was a barn.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But she went out to get-- to dig this money up.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was, again, one of those horrifying nights for me that I remember.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was-- I was covered with a blanket in this dark, miserable place.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there were rats and mice all over.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
